== New Release Version of OwnRide ==
hnote across: When a new release extracts more data in a newer version, existing "extracted" \ndata is not changed. This is what the recalculate endpoint is responsible for.

Caller -> API: <b>PUT</b> /own/activities/{id}/recalculate
